# NEUBIAS Training Modules Integration

This directory contains adaptations and extensions of the excellent NEUBIAS Training Resources for bioimage analysis. The original modules can be found at [NEUBIAS Training Resources](https://neubias.github.io/training-resources/all-modules/).

## Directory Structure

```
neubias-modules/
├── README.md                                  # This file - overview and credits
├── introductory/
│   ├── pixels_and_images.md                   # Introduction to digital images
│   ├── image_display.ipynb                    # Image visualization techniques
│   └── pixel_inspection.ipynb                 # Pixel value analysis
├── preprocessing/
│   ├── binarization.ipynb                     # Thresholding methods
│   ├── noise_filtering.ipynb                  # Denoising approaches
│   └── background_correction.ipynb            # Background estimation and removal
├── segmentation/
│   ├── connected_components.ipynb             # Basic object identification
│   ├── semantic_segmentation.ipynb            # Pixel classification methods
│   └── instance_segmentation.ipynb            # Object instance separation
├── feature_extraction/
│   ├── intensity_measurements.ipynb           # Quantifying signal intensity
│   ├── shape_descriptors.ipynb                # Morphological measurements
│   └── texture_analysis.ipynb                 # Pattern and texture features
├── workflows/
│   ├── cell_counting.ipynb                    # Complete cell detection workflow
│   ├── timelapse_tracking.ipynb               # Temporal object tracking
│   └── colocalization_analysis.ipynb          # Multi-channel correlation analysis
└── data/
    └── neubias_samples/                       # Sample images from NEUBIAS
```

